snippet.title: Episode 10: Birds of Prey Review, Trailers, Warcraft Reforged, and Should Amber Heard Be Replaced?
snippet.description:
Thank you for joining us on our quest to expel the darkness from all of Geekdom!

Today, Paladin Ashley gives a brief spoiler free Birds of Prey review, we talk trailers, Warcraft Reforged, and whether Amber Heard should be replaced as Mera in Aquaman 2!

Subscribe today to become a Knight in our Medieval army! It’s that easy!

You can also follow us on social media:
Twitter: www.twitter.com/radiantpodcast 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/radiantdamagepodcast

Or support us on Patreon to unlock some exclusive perks!
https://www.patreon.com/radiantdamagepodcast

Thanks again for watching! 
Godspeed and Excelsior!
